rows.label: campfev11_140_150_msg0001
rows.name:
Laura-sama! Your mother is safe and
sound at Trigo Village!

rows.label: campfev11_140_150_msg0002
rows.name: That's at the Gulan border, I believe.

rows.label: campfev11_140_150_msg0003
rows.name:
That's right. We can make our way
via the ferry from Yanchik Harbor.

rows.label: campfev11_140_150_msg0004
rows.name:
Then I guess we need to stop chewing
the fat and head out to Gulan!

rows.label: campfev11_140_150_msg0005
rows.name: You're really coming with us, Adel?

rows.label: campfev11_140_150_msg0006
rows.name: Hey. My word is my bond.

rows.label: campfev11_140_150_msg0007
rows.name:
I am worried about my mother, sure,
but is this really what we should be
doing right now...?
